nodes.html: A perfect blend of personalities and visions from two souls with the same perspective but different realities whos constant pursuit to achieve their fullest potential pushes them to greater heights and planes of existence and effort. Renoir and Uncle Jo, two artist with distinct styles merge to form a single tag team duo of high flying syllables, death defying beats and a passion for life that is unmatched. Krisscross is the ultimate celebrating of collaboration and their debut release is set in winter.

Forged from fire, built from bricks, set in success a group of spirted, determined, persistent souls who mission in life is to share their pain, emotions, thoughts and love with the world. To be a London Fog Boi is to be someone of great character willing to weather any storm which is why we named ourselves after the most durable, comfortable and iconic clothing brand London Fog. A constant rotation of new ideas, energy and projects comes out of this group and their debut album is set to release in mid 2022.Â

The Renowned Renoir is the journey of one beings path to find himself. He is a relentless individual whos pursuit to put his own work out into lead the thesis of Renowned, pushing friend, colleagues, and others to put their life's work out. Renowned is a place for artist built by artist for artist. Renoir is an artist in his own right and just recently released his second album the first in five years Pride which is a collection of songs made over the past fiver years. Renoir plans on building out the rest of Renowned in the coming quarters and soon will have it on the map as the curator of culture, a place made to leave indelible mark just like he envisioned all those years ago when he would daydream in his room.
